### рџ“€ Insight 2: Margin Improves as Product Mix Diversifies

| Period | Gross Margin |
|--------|-------------|
| 2015 (Bikes only) | ~40.3% |
| 2016 H1 | ~42.2% |
| 2016 H2 onwards | ~42.5вЂ“43.3% |

Bikes carry 38вЂ“45% margin. Accessories carry 58вЂ“64% margin. As the accessory and clothing mix grew post-July 2016, blended margin improved by ~3 percentage points. This is a structurally important insight вЂ” growing non-Bike categories is not just a volume story, it is a **margin expansion story**.

