### рџ”„ Insight 7: Return Rate Is Healthy at 2.17%

1,828 units returned out of 84,174 sold = **2.17% return rate**. For a specialty physical goods retailer selling high-value items ($295 avg unit price), this is a strong result. Returns are distributed proportionally to sales volume вЂ” no category or territory shows an abnormal spike.

